[
  {
    "id": "kp-5.1-01",
    "section": "5.1",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Units of Measure and Conversions",
    "title_zh": "计量单位与单位换算",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "In mensuration, it is crucial to use consistent units for calculations. The metric system is standard in IGCSE.\n\n**Linear units** (Length) include millimeters ($mm$), centimeters ($cm$), meters ($m$), and kilometers ($km$). $10\\,mm = 1\\,cm$, $100\\,cm = 1\\,m$, $1000\\,m = 1\\,km$.\n\n**Area units** are squared units like $cm^2$ or $m^2$. When converting area, you must square the linear conversion factor. For example, since $1\\,m = 100\\,cm$, then $1\\,m^2 = 100^2\\,cm^2 = 10,000\\,cm^2$.\n\n**Volume units** are cubed units like $cm^3$ or $m^3$. When converting volume, cube the linear conversion factor. Since $1\\,cm = 10\\,mm$, then $1\\,cm^3 = 10^3\\,mm^3 = 1,000\\,mm^3$. Note that $1\\,cm^3 = 1\\,ml$ and $1,000\\,cm^3 = 1\\,litre$.",
      "zh": "在几何测量中，计算时使用统一的单位至关重要。IGCSE 考试标准使用公制单位。\n\n**长度单位** 包括毫米 ($mm$)、厘米 ($cm$)、米 ($m$) 和千米 ($km$)。换算关系为：$10\\,mm = 1\\,cm$，$100\\,cm = 1\\,m$，$1000\\,m = 1\\,km$。\n\n**面积单位** 使用平方单位，如 $cm^2$ 或 $m^2$。转换面积单位时，必须将长度换算系数平方。例如，因为 $1\\,m = 100\\,cm$，所以 $1\\,m^2 = 100^2\\,cm^2 = 10,000\\,cm^2$。\n\n**体积单位** 使用立方单位，如 $cm^3$ 或 $m^3$。转换体积单位时，将长度换算系数立方。例如，因为 $1\\,cm = 10\\,mm$，所以 $1\\,cm^3 = 10^3\\,mm^3 = 1,000\\,mm^3$。注意 $1\\,cm^3 = 1\\,ml$ 且 $1,000\\,cm^3 = 1\\,升(litre)$。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-unit-conv",
        "label": "Convert between area or volume units",
        "label_zh": "面积或体积单位换算",
        "description": "Convert values from $m^2$ to $cm^2$ or $cm^3$ to $litres$ to prepare for calculations.",
        "description_zh": "在计算前将数值从 $m^2$ 转换为 $cm^2$ 或从 $cm^3$ 转换为升。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-unit-conv",
        "question": "A floor has an area of $12\\,m^2$. Calculate the area in $cm^2$.",
        "question_zh": "一个地板的面积为 $12\\,m^2$。请计算其以 $cm^2$ 为单位的面积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Recall the linear conversion: $1\\,m = 100\\,cm$.\n\n**Step 2:** Determine the area conversion factor: $1\\,m^2 = 100 \\times 100\\,cm^2 = 10,000\\,cm^2$.\n\n**Step 3:** Multiply the given area by the factor: $12 \\times 10,000 = 120,000\\,cm^2$.\n\n**Answer:** $120,000\\,cm^2$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 回想长度换算：$1\\,m = 100\\,cm$。\n\n**步骤2：** 确定面积换算系数：$1\\,m^2 = 100 \\times 100\\,cm^2 = 10,000\\,cm^2$。\n\n**步骤3：** 将给定面积乘以系数：$12 \\times 10,000 = 120,000\\,cm^2$。\n\n**答案：** $120,000\\,cm^2$",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580/21/M/J/20"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "How many $mm^3$ are in $5\\,cm^3$?",
        "q_zh": "$5\\,cm^3$ 等于多少 $mm^3$？",
        "o": [
          "50",
          "500",
          "5,000",
          "50,000"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "$1\\,cm = 10\\,mm$, so $1\\,cm^3 = 10^3\\,mm^3 = 1,000\\,mm^3$. Therefore, $5\\,cm^3 = 5 \\times 1,000 = 5,000\\,mm^3$.",
        "e_zh": "$1\\,cm = 10\\,mm$，所以 $1\\,cm^3 = 10^3\\,mm^3 = 1,000\\,mm^3$。因此，$5\\,cm^3 = 5 \\times 1,000 = 5,000\\,mm^3$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "Convert $0.8\\,litres$ into $cm^3$.",
        "q_zh": "将 $0.8$ 升转换为 $cm^3$。",
        "o": [
          "8",
          "80",
          "800",
          "8,000"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "$1\\,litre = 1,000\\,cm^3$. So, $0.8 \\times 1,000 = 800\\,cm^3$.",
        "e_zh": "$1$ 升 $= 1,000\\,cm^3$。所以，$0.8 \\times 1,000 = 800\\,cm^3$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "metric-units"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
