  {
    "id": "kp-5.4-01",
    "section": "5.4",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Prisms and Cylinders",
    "title_zh": "柱体与圆柱体",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "A **prism** is a 3D shape with a constant cross-section.\n\n**Volume of a prism** is calculated by: $Volume = Area\\ of\\ cross\\!-\\!section \\times length$.\n\n**Cylinders** are special prisms with a circular cross-section. \nVolume ($V$) = $\\pi r^2 h$.\nCurved Surface Area ($CSA$) = $2\\pi rh$.\nTotal Surface Area ($TSA$) = $2\\pi rh + 2\\pi r^2$ (curved area + two circular ends).",
      "zh": "**柱体** 是具有恒定横截面的三维图形。\n\n**柱体的体积** 计算公式为：$体积 = 横截面面积 \\times 长度$。\n\n**圆柱体** 是具有圆形横截面的特殊柱体。\n体积 ($V$) = $\\pi r^2 h$。\n侧面积 ($CSA$) = $2\\pi rh$。\n全表面积 ($TSA$) = $2\\pi rh + 2\\pi r^2$（侧面积 + 两个圆底面积）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-cylinder-volume",
        "label": "Calculate cylinder volume or height",
        "label_zh": "计算圆柱体积或高度",
        "description": "Use $V = \\pi r^2 h$ to find volume, or rearrange to find $h = \\frac{V}{\\pi r^2}$.",
        "description_zh": "使用 $V = \\pi r^2 h$ 求体积，或变形求高度 $h = \\frac{V}{\\pi r^2}$。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-cylinder-volume",
        "question": "A cylinder has a height of $10\\,cm$ and a radius of $4\\,cm$. Calculate its volume.",
        "question_zh": "一个圆柱体的高度为 $10\\,cm$，半径为 $4\\,cm$。计算其体积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use $V = \\pi r^2 h$.\n\n**Step 2:** Substitute values: $V = \\pi \\times 4^2 \\times 10 = 160\\pi$.\n\n**Step 3:** $160 \\times 3.14159 \\approx 502.7\\,cm^3$.\n\n**Answer:** $503\\,cm^3$ (to 3 s.f.)",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用 $V = \\pi r^2 h$。\n\n**步骤2：** 代入数值：$V = \\pi \\times 4^2 \\times 10 = 160\\pi$。\n\n**步骤3：** $160 \\times 3.14159 \\approx 502.7\\,cm^3$。\n\n**答案：** $503\\,cm^3$（保留 3 位有效数字）",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580/42/M/J/17"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "The total surface area of a closed cylinder with radius $r$ and height $h$ is given by:",
        "q_zh": "半径为 $r$、高度为 $h$ 的封闭圆柱体的全表面积公式是：",
        "o": [
          "$\\pi r^2 h$",
