          "$2\\pi rh + 2\\pi r^2$"
        ],
        "a": 3,
        "e": "A closed cylinder has a curved surface ($2\\pi rh$) and two circular ends ($2 \\times \\pi r^2$).",
        "e_zh": "封闭圆柱体包含一个侧面 ($2\\pi rh$) 和两个圆形底面 ($2 \\times \\pi r^2$)。"
      }
    ],
