        "label_zh": "计算阴影面积",
        "description": "Subtract the area of inner shapes from the outer shape (e.g., circle inside a square).",
        "description_zh": "从外部图形面积中减去内部图形面积（例如：正方形内含圆）。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
